description: I was very pleased with the expertise I received during my call. She was very professional and I would have given her 5 stars if it was available.
Shopping was easy and convenient. Price was half of what I found on other sites. Seems like shipping is pretty fast, I will see.
Can't reach anyone to get return authorization. They keep you on the phone forever and tell you the wait time is 2 minutes and you wait a half hour and hear the same lie--two minutes
The part arrived in good time and was correct. I installed the starter and with the first turn of the key fired up the engine! Thankyou.
